  "notes": "Captures Admin GraphQL 2026-04 priceListUpdate behavior for a disposable price list attached to a disposable market catalog after adding two variant fixed prices. Shopify preserves fixed prices for same-currency updates, leaves currency and fixed prices intact for rejected parent-adjustment updates, and clears the fixed-price connection/count when the currency changes while preserving parent adjustment and catalog relation. The local proxy replays setup through public reads/mutations; the variant hydrate read warms observed ProductVariant state so fixed-price mutations do not require hidden store setup."
